com.gwtplatform.dispatch.server
Interface Dispatch

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDispatchImpl, DispatchImpl, DispatchImpl
public interface Dispatch

The base class of the synchronous dispatcher service with an arbitrary action type. The server-side implementation is DispatchImpl and the async client-side version is DispatchAsync.

This class is closely related to com.gwtplatform.dispatch.server.DispatchService. In fact, this class wouldn't be needed, but we use it to workaround a GWT limitation described in DispatchAsync.

Author:
Christian Goudreau, David Peterson
